te this question by focusing on a single lineage of polyomaviruses that infect both humans and their closest relatives, the African great apes. We show that these viruses exhibit considerable host specificity and that their evolution largely mirrors that of their hosts, suggesting that codivergence with their hosts played a major role in their diversification. Our results provide statistical evidence in favor of an association of polyomaviruses and their hosts over millions of years.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Madinda, Nad\u00e8ge F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ehlers, Bernhard", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wertheim, Joel O.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Akoua-Koffi, Chantal", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bergl, Richard A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Boesch, Christophe", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Akonkwa, Dieudonn\u00e9 Boji Mungu", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Eckardt, Winnie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fruth, Barbara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gillespie, Thomas R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gray, Maryke", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hohmann, Gottfried", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Karhemere, Stomy", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kujirakwinja, Deo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Langergraber, Kevin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Muyembe, Jean-Jacques", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nishuli, Radar", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pauly, Maude", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Petrzelkova, Klara J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Robbins, Martha M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Todd, Angelique", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schubert, Grit", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stoinski, Tara S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wittig, Roman M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zuberb\u00fchler, Klaus", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Peeters, Martine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Leendertz, Fabian H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Calvignac-Spencer, S\u00e9ba